{"tid":216160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【AA制出事】「牛角」老闆show帳單 爆出驚人真相","createTime":"2017-04-25T02:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-25T02:51:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6cebfa7b695983865271b8d3dc12ae34beb7b0ed","tid":216160,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T02:50:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170425&amp;guid=56609541&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170425%26guid%3D56609541%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=43737a14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170425%26guid%3D56609541%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=28b01246\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170425&amp;guid=56609541&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n【AA制出事】「牛角」老闆show帳單 爆出驚人真相<br />\n<br />\n即時突發&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n2017-04-25 10:05:41 HKT<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n黃傑龍(小圖)今早在facebook貼出該對男女的帳單(左圖)<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n兩人單單飲品已經差不多1200元，而食物則只點了700多元，結帳總數2135.1元。<br />\n<br />\n有「中古王」之稱的37歲玩具店老闆，前晚與新相識38歲女子在日本燒肉店「牛角」食晚飯時，因「AA制」問題而大打出手，事件經報道後(&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2pXI7Ep￼&nbsp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2pXI7Ep%EF%BF%BC%C2%A0&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=90771aaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2pXI7Ep￼&nbsp;</a>)成為城中熱話。就連身在日本開會的「牛角」老闆黃傑龍(&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bit.ly/1ehoOi4￼&nbsp;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1ehoOi4%EF%BF%BC%C2%A0&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=1d3192ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/1ehoOi4￼&nbsp;</a>)亦有留意這宗新聞，更越洋致電同事了解內情，結果獲悉提出「AA制」的竟然是女方。<br />\n<br />\n黃傑龍今早在facebook貼出該對男女的帳單（&nbsp;<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2pYNWkY￼&nbsp;），指兩人於晚上7時54分入座，吃了三個多小時，一共點了3支sake、3杯啤酒，連同汽水在內，單單飲品已經差不多1200元，而食物則只點了700多元，結帳總數2135.1元。黃傑龍稱，向同事了解後得知兩人「基本上係食晒冇浪費嘅」。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2pYNWkY%EF%BF%BC%C2%A0%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%8C%E6%8C%87%E5%85%A9%E4%BA%BA%E6%96%BC%E6%99%9A%E4%B8%8A7%E6%99%8254%E5%88%86%E5%85%A5%E5%BA%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%83%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%89%E5%80%8B%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%85%B1%E9%BB%9E%E4%BA%863%E6%94%AFsake%E3%80%813%E6%9D%AF%E5%95%A4%E9%85%92%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%A3%E5%90%8C%E6%B1%BD%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%A8%E5%85%A7%EF%BC%8C%E5%96%AE%E5%96%AE%E9%A3%B2%E5%93%81%E5%B7%B2%E7%B6%93%E5%B7%AE%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%9A1200%E5%85%83%EF%BC%8C%E8%80%8C%E9%A3%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%89%87%E5%8F%AA%E9%BB%9E%E4%BA%86700%E5%A4%9A%E5%85%83%EF%BC%8C%E7%B5%90%E5%B8%B3%E7%B8%BD%E6%95%B82135.1%E5%85%83%E3%80%82%E9%BB%83%E5%82%91%E9%BE%8D%E7%A8%B1%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%91%E5%90%8C%E4%BA%8B%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%BE%8C%E5%BE%97%E7%9F%A5%E5%85%A9%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%8C%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8A%E4%BF%82%E9%A3%9F%E6%99%92%E5%86%87%E6%B5%AA%E8%B2%BB%E5%98%85%E3%80%8D%E3%80%82&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21L%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=811bd0d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2pYNWkY￼&nbsp;），指兩人於晚上7時54分入座，吃了三個多小時，一共點了3支sake、3杯啤酒，連同汽水在內，單單飲品已經差不多1200元，而食物則只點了700多元，結帳總數2135.1元。黃傑龍稱，向同事了解後得知兩人「基本上係食晒冇浪費嘅」。</a><br />\n<br />\n黃傑龍稱，結帳時，是男子以現金付款，但女子則禮貌地提出「AA制」，不過男子表現豪氣拒絕，而女子卻拿出一張500元現金給對方，豈料此一舉動卻惹怒了男子，男子當場撕爛張銀紙。由於警方正在調查事件，黃傑龍不方便多講「然後嘅事」，只表示最後是由男子以2,200元現金結帳，包括貼士60多元。<br />\n<br />\n黃傑龍以「好可愛」形容兩人，認為他們都是性情中人，祝福兩人可以繼續做到好朋友。<br />\n<br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 即Call《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線 ：63836568<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n經理：酒類佔賬單大部份<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;4小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\nAA制＝夾錢　70年代起流行<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;4小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n【約嗰個畀晒？】AA制不如AB制？　約會前講清楚好啲<br />\n<br />\n文化&nbsp;4小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br 